description:
This feature includes registering, Modifying and Approval of Business Admin and 
    Customer Support Admin Users by System Admin
name: System Admin My Activity

elements.name: To verify that system user can manage user registration application, which are not approved like saved,submitted users and rejected users

steps.name: Login into Mobiquity Portal as System admin Maker
Navigate to User Management and Click on register
Select User type as Adminstrator and click on Customer care Admin
Navigate to My Activity and Add the required filter
Click on Expand and View Details button

elements.name: To verify that system user can view existing details of user's under saved filter whose registration initiation is incomplete

steps.name: Login into Mobiquity Portal as System admin Maker
Navigate to My Activity and Add the required filter
Click on Expand and View Details button

elements.name: To verify that system user can Add/edit details of user's whose registration is incomplete

steps.name: Login into Mobiquity Portal as System admin Maker
Navigate to My Activity and Add the required filter
Click on Expand and Resume button
Enter all the required details of the user
